Function Documentation

int32_t PmlibVideopllGetpllStructure ( uint32_t  freq,
uint32_t  maxOrMinMN,
pmhalPrcmDpllConfig_t *  pllParams,
uint32_t *  postDivider 
)

Api to gets the VideoPll structure for given frequency .

Parameters
freqFrequency at which video pll needs to be configured.
maxOrMinMNThis parameter allows the API to calculate the maximum value of M and N for the given frequency or minimum value of M and N for the given frequency. 0U - Minimum value of M and N. 1U - Maximum value of M and N.
pllParamsVideopll params structure
postDividerPost divider structure.
Returns
status Returns the status of the API. This can be the following values: PM_SUCCESS If the desired frequency was set. PM_FAIL If the desired frequency was not set.
